renderables.text: This master ticket or ownership seed could be used to transfer ownership or impersonate your planet on the Urbit network without your permission.
If you lose a child seed, you can recover it from your master ticket or ownership seed.
The ownership seed is a BIP39 mnemonic, which can be used as the master seed for a hardware wallet.

The Master Ticket and Ownership seed can be used to recover Transfer Proxy, Spawn, Delegate, and Management Seeds.
Use the master ticket or ownership seed to Boot, Transfer, Escape to a new sponsor, Set up transfer and management proxies, Re-key, and Recover child seeds.
This is the most critical part of the HD Wallet to store securely. This ticket can authenticate any wallet action or rekey an entire wallet from scratch.
Store cold in a paper or hardware wallet away from other seeds.
